OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly frost and fog clearing to
OL,6,Fleave plenty of sunshine on Sunday
OL,7,Fmorning. Cloud bubbling up during the
OL,8,Fday, giving way to sunny spells, and
OL,9,Fthere will be a few showers, mainly in
OL,10,Fthe north. Feeling pleasant with light
OL,11,Fwinds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry for most this evening
OL,14,Fwith lengthy clear skies and fog
OL,15,Fpatches in Northern Ireland. Cloudier
OL,16,Fin the far northeast with showers or
OL,17,Flonger spells of rain. Frost in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
