OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA chilly start with any fog
OL,6,Fclearing. Dry in the west and in
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland with sunny spells.
OL,8,FCloudier in the east with showers
OL,9,Fspreading westwards through the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
